fileChanges.details:
Add a @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) block that:
1. Sets .swiper-wrapper transition-duration to 0ms (overrides Swiper's inline style)
2. Disables the carousel-nav-btn gradient sweep animation
3. Disables the swiper-pagination-progressbar-fill transition

This is a theme-wide fix that benefits all carousels (CardsCarousel, TestimonialsCarousel, DynamicContentCarousel) since they all use swiper.css.

Example:
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .swiper-wrapper { transition-duration: 0ms !important; }
  .carousel-nav-btn::before { transition: none; animation: none; }
  .swiper-pagination-progressbar .swiper-pagination-progressbar-fill { transition: none; }
}
